snippet.title: Doom 2: Junkfood 3 Wad Trailer
snippet.description:
Downloab: https://www.doomworld.com/forum/topic/144406

Junk Food 3 is a MBF21-compatible Speedmapping Community Project held in the Pacifist Paradise Discord Server. The basic premise was to make cowboy-themed "Junk Food" slaughter (BFG spammy, high monster count maps) where not a lot of time is spent deliberating about layout/detailing/fight design/other things that can bog a mapper down. It's just good BFG fun.

Music Credits: "Wow Wow" by Neil Cicierega - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CPhXKak_bHw
